  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  History of cytological or histological documentation of non-metastatic extremity
             osteosarcoma.

          -  5-21 years of age.

          -  Subject is eligible for routine chemotherapy and routine surgery for the treatment of
             non-metastatic extremity osteosarcoma

          -  Informed consent is obtained

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Females with a positive urine pregnancy test.

          -  Unable to comply with study procedures
      </textblock>
